RESOURCE.DESCRIPTION: By downloading SkyMapper data you agree to observe the policies published at http://skymapper.anu.edu.au/policies/

PARAM.name: Service Name
PARAM.value: SkyMapper DR2 Simple Image Access Service (Public Access)

FIELD.name: ra_cntr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ICRS Right Ascension of the image centre

FIELD.name: dec_cntr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ICRS Declination of the image centre

FIELD.name: mjd_obs
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Modified Julian Date of exposure start

FIELD.name: scale
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: WCS pixel scale of each image axis

FIELD.name: pixflags
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Pixel flags of source image (C=raw cutout, V=suitable for visualisation only)

FIELD.name: mean_fwhm
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Mean image seeing FWHM as calculated by Science Data Pipeline

FIELD.name: mean_elong
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Mean image source elongation as calculated by Science Data Pipeline

FIELD.name: zpapprox
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Approximate frame zeropoint. Refer to docs for more info.

FIELD.name: crpix
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Pixel coordinates of the WCS reference pixel

FIELD.name: crval
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: World coordinates of the WCS reference pixel

FIELD.name: cdmatrix
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: WCS CD matrix. Elements are ordered as CD[i,j] = [1,1], [1,2], [2,1], [2,2]

PARAM.name: proj
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Tangent plane projection with a polynomial distortion function described by coefficients provided in a set of PVi_j keywords. The first image axis represents Right Ascension and the second represents Declination
